InMemoryMapKeyValueStore<K,V>
@ApiAudience.Public
@ApiStability.Experimental
public static final class InMemoryMapKeyValueStore.Builder<K,V>
extends Object

A Builder-pattern class that configures and creates new InMemoryMapKeyValueStore instances. Use this to specify the Map<String, String> for this KeyValueStore and call build() to return a new instance.

Method Detail

withMap

public InMemoryMapKeyValueStore.Builder withMap(Map<K,V> map)
Sets the map containing the keys and values. Its contents will be copied at the call to build(). This is a shallow copy: Updates to the map will not be reflected after build(), but mutations to keys and values will until the InMemoryMapKeyValueStore is serialized into a Configuration.

Parameters:
map - the map containing the data backing this key value store.
Returns:
this builder instance.

an initialized KeyValueStore.
